<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīveṁkkaṭēśāya maṁggaḷaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="2"/>śrīmadbaṁddārunagarē viśṛtōnaṁtapaṁḍitaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> muḍuṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>bavaṁśaja<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīmān dhīra<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied>śrīvatsagōtrakaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasyābhūda
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁmmamākhyāyāṁ sutastaṁmappapaṁḍitaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tasya veṁkkaṭakri
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṣṇā<unclear>khyā</unclear> vallamāyāmajāyata [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] tasyāsan raṁgamā<unclear>khyā</unclear>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>yāṁ sutāḥ paṁcca guṇōttarāḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> veṁkkaṭādhīśvaraścāppako
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁḍḍappastadanaṁtaraṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3*] veṁgaḷappaścavallappatiṁmmappa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ścēti viśṛtāḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tēṣāṁ madhyētu timmappassuprabhā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>vō dayānidhiḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4*] yēna durgāṇyaraṇyāni nagarāṇyabhava
<lb n="10" break="no"/>n bhuvi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nirjalassajalaścāsītpāṣāṇā dēvatāgṛhā<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 5*] sō
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yaṁ timapanāmārya<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> vēṇīsāgarasaṁggamō <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> gaṇapatyā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>khyakaṁ liṁgaṁ cōḍarājapratiṣṭhitaṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 6*] śarākāśarttu<unclear>śītāṁśu</unclear>
<lb n="13" break="no"/>yutaśākē śubhāvahē dvādasyāṁ rudhirōdgārimādhavē sitē
<lb n="14" break="no"/>pakṣēkarōnmahābhāgaṁ supratiṣṭhitamavyayaṁ
<lb n="15"/>vaiṣṇavaṁ vigra<unclear>haṁ</unclear> cāpi lakṣyāṁ veṁkaṭakriṣṇakaḥ [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 7*]
<lb n="16"/>kāśācāri mummaḍiśiṁggu liṁgābattuḍu
<lb n="17"/>Itanibhārya liṁggayiri komā
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ruṁḍu kōllābattuḍu
<lb n="19"/>yita<supplied reason="omitted">ni</supplied> bhārya rudrama Iri ko
<lb n="20" break="no"/>māruṁḍu kāmākṣi yitani bhārya pārvati
<lb n="21"/>Iri komāllu mallaya nāgappa śarabhaya
<lb n="22"/>vīrappa <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

